{"tid":1426910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民水軍:我覺得真係要聽吓劉世良 我:我覺得真係要聽吓毛澤東","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:29:05.000Z","uid":272968,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd920906b31d3f7d7379241da1b0f04614b74fb1","tid":1426910,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:17:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命無罪，造反有理</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6300887ed9e35396d29683347bf96bc509eee8ef","tid":1426910,"uid":35699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:24:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果他們要打，就把他們徹底消滅。<br />\n事情就是這樣，他來進攻，我們把他消滅了，他就舒服了。<br />\n消滅一點，舒服一點；<br />\n消滅得多，舒服得多；<br />\n徹底消滅，徹底舒服。<br />\n<br />\n中國的問題是覆雜的，我們的腦子也要覆雜一點。<br />\n人家打來了,我們就打,打是為了爭取和平。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《關於重慶談判》（一九四五年十月十七日），《毛澤東選集》第四卷第一一五八頁"},{"pid":"46cceace3db58cafe0a93439817d191ea23a5888","tid":1426910,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"複雜"},{"pid":"284240ff91eb942b9666529cc7cd8eeba8dcde57","tid":1426910,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"政治就是把自己人搞得多多的，把對方的人搞得少少的"},{"pid":"602f306eddf264040a8cd5683e15879431f47982","tid":1426910,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命無罪，造反有理</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}